OL,3,C86-year-old golfer living with
OL,4,Carthritis wins first-place trophy in
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FAn 86-year-old woman has triumphed at
OL,8,Fa golf tournament in north Wales.
OL,10,FGladys Hughes, from Llanrwst, secured
OL,11,Ffirst place at the Royal Oak Bowl at
OL,12,FBetws-Y-Coed Golf Club, with a nett
OL,13,Fscore of 68.
OL,15,FDespite living with arthritis that
OL,16,Faffects her hands, she says the
OL,17,Fcondition "doesn't stop me from
OL,18,Fplaying golf," and was "over the moon"
OL,19,Fto receive the trophy.
