OL,3,C86-year-old golfer living with
OL,4,Carthritis wins first-place trophy in
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FGladys has been playing golf for more
OL,8,Fthan 45 years, having first taken up
OL,9,Fthe sport on the advice of her doctor
OL,10,Fto help improve her health.
OL,12,FReflecting on her victory, she said:
OL,13,F"It can be very painful, but I know if
OL,14,FI persevere, it feels better."
OL,16,FShe added: "I am thrilled to win the
OL,17,FCup. I'd considered retiring from golf
OL,18,Fearlier in the year as my hands and
OL,19,Flegs were really painful. I'm so
OL,20,Fpleased I didn't give up!"
