OL,7,FGladys, who lives at Hafan Gwydir
OL,8,Findependent living scheme in Llanrwst,
OL,9,Fhas been described as an inspiration.
OL,11,FManager Sian Taylor said: "We are
OL,12,Fabsolutely delighted for Gladys! She's
OL,13,Fincredibly energetic and motivates
OL,14,Fmany of our residents and staff to
OL,15,Ffollow in her footsteps!"
